Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to prosper while so far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By following a drama's fable,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We get thrown into a red-tainted case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, be careful up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat with the glasses, how's it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, is this how you thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that brat needs to grow up sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it really up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Sonoko's red handkerchief up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the red one, the red one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My red handkerchief blew into that tree, I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why I'm up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the wind blew it away, I'm\Npretty sure it got stuck in that tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that the wind blew it away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't think it tied it to this branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Did you find it or not? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.40,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, glasses-wearing brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be the thing you're standing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Standing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like... We found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko's Red Handkerchief, Part One!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You gonna tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez... Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What made you want to visit this maple forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, see this red handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should know just by seeing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:05:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you at least recognize the title, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Title?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Maple Leaves of Winter."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's, "The Maple Leaves of Winter."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last year's most popular romantic drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you didn't watch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you into those?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it came on during a show in which Okino Youko\Nwas singing, so dad was watching and taping that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle and Okino Youko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, about the drama and the red handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they related?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid like you wouldn't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} will explain anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It involves an army officer and a wealthy daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love and romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They met for the first time when he retrieved her handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a maple tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was a senior officer who was jealous of their love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he filed an unjustified charge against him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forcing him to flee abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when the war was over, she received a telegram from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"On Hatsuzora, wait under the the maple leaves."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, doesn't "hatsuzora" refer to the first sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the maple leaves are gone during winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knew he meant the forest where they first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She couldn't remember exactly where,\Nso she walked all over the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she only found dead trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She found out that there were no\Nmaple leaves during hatsuzora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was about to give up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was sure he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amidst the snow, tied to a branch, was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A red handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bright red handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, they reunited under that tree on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They decided to elope...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And lived happily ever after!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the officer is dark skinned, speaks\Nsimply, and is just all around cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Kyougoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right, that's just it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I watched it again on DVD and it reminded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fable with so much love and romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just like me and Makato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, the reason I came up here to where the drama was shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna put up my own red handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so you can meet Kyougoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is it okay to do that without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm only gonna put up one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, someone will notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? Something we don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are red handerkerchiefs everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, is this where they shot that drama scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the last scene, the officer was\Nwaiting with his back to a big rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:09:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words: You weren't the only one that thought of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already mailed Makato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll be waiting under the maple leaves on the eve."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you go again, Sonoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With your puzzling messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there are so many handkerchiefs here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two will have to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be my handkerchief or there's no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I found something earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that tree I just climbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a red handkerchief tied to a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was pretty far from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if they are tied to trees all over this mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where will I wait for Makato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think, before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should consider whether a martial arts type\Nof guy like him could get this maple leaves hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, glasses-wearing brat, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're taking down all of these red handkerchiefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I must have our destined meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, you shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my fault this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you taking down the handkerchief's\Nbecause you can't see the maple leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By saying it's your fault, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The writer of "The Maple Leaves of Winter?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, I'm just on the drama's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assistant Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just an assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry for ruining your view.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But one of the writers asked me if knew of a\Nmaple leaf forest to be used in a drama series.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I suggested we use this range.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this is near my hometown, I played here as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while I was scouting out the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a red handkerchief tied to a maple tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I reported this to the writer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He decided to include it in the script, creating a powerful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, it became popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People began camping here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even began tieing red handkerchiefs up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This made the owner of this mountain angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Are you trying to cover my mountain in handkerchiefs!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, then again, the inn and shop owners\Nare satisfied with all of the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not many came here unless it was maple season.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'm the one who handles requests about which\Nmountain it was from the TV reporters and fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Where is the mountain you filmed on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Where did you film the last scene?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, just today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fan offered to pay me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to find the tree which the original handkerchief was tied to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I set out to find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could you pass on a message for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot the fan's phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of the train station, you'll find\NAkagi Inn, which has a guest notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:13:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I found the tree you seek. Meet me at the\Nrock used for the drama's last scene."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need you to write that there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The original plan was for me to meet the\Nfan at the inn and escort them to the tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it'd be hard on me to walk down there\Nfor our meeting and then escort them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the way back up here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we should leave your name with the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Hozumi."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Write it in katakana and I'm sure they'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want it written in katakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've only spoken with that person over the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can tell they are a big fan of\Nthe drama and come here often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from that, the mail I got earlier\Nindicated they're already there waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I told them I'd write in the\Nnotebook if something went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll see you all later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I found the tree you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Meet me at the rock used for the drama's last scene."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Hozumi."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Sonoko, want to eat here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what're you in the mood for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it'd be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've barely moved your chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tie this handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her sudden impulses as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, you planned to wear your favorite color, red,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To meet up with Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he saw a cute girl wearing red go by and followed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got to meet him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you forgot to wear red.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the exact same scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't take much to get her going, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there are red handkerchiefs tied up everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't know which was Sonoko-neechan's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I added my name to it and made it look like a flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now there's no way Makato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} can miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There goes "The Maple Leaves of Winter" plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's getting dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ghosts might come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this belong to that assistant director?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must've dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's blood on the calendar section.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he smeared it with his finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why April 1st?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's kind of wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can just put it in the lost box later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back here, glasses-wearing brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you were running!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could this have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was fine earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body's still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was killed under thirty minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's dirt under his nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's dirt doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dirt under his nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood on the calendar section...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Specifically on April 1st...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is Hozumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found a man who's been stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not just one or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)}What the...
